{"tid":2159120,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港竟然有黃既日籍插畫家","createTime":"2020-08-16T06:34:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T06:34:12.000Z","uid":90282,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8a3f5462a9c03601c53dd20d753e19323e08703b","tid":2159120,"uid":90282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:34:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\">國安法襲港，外國紛紛打開大門招手，不少港人心灰意冷，熱議移民各地。過去一年，參與了很多次反修例運動遊行的奈緒子，卻想繼續留守香港，「和香港有很大的不同，日本人沒有移民的想法。當自己的家遇到問題，會努力改善，不是離家出走。」</span><br />\n<br />\n逐漸受年輕人鼓舞之下，她也開始能理解香港人的「勇氣」。大部分遊行奈緒子都參與了，有一次雙方情勢膠著，地鐵站都全部關閉，她一度很害怕，心裏不斷想：「我回不去怎麼辦？」但她明白，當下應該繼續堅持，「因為我知道，我應該站在這裡，跟香港人一起保護這個地方。」與在場的示威者一樣，「我已經把香港當成是自己的地方。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/66055460_2512733888779509_4291782204087861248_o_7eLFn_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F66055460_2512733888779509_4291782204087861248_o_7eLFn_1200x0.jpg&h=70313b20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【專訪】當國安法掀起移民潮 居港日籍插畫家：留下，因為這是我的家<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E6%8E%80%E8%B5%B7%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E6%BD%AE-%E5%B1%85%E6%B8%AF%E6%97%A5%E7%B1%8D%E6%8F%92%E7%95%AB%E5%AE%B6-%E7%95%99%E4%B8%8B%E5%9B%A0%E7%82%BA%E9%80%99%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%B6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%258E%2580%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%25BD%25AE-%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%25B1%258D%25E6%258F%2592%25E7%2595%25AB%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E7%2595%2599%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%259B%25A0%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%2580%2599%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25AE%25B6%2F&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJAp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=ea1abe2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%258E%2580%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%25BD%25AE-%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%25B1%258D%25E6%258F%2592%25E7%2595%25AB%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E7%2595%2599%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%259B%25A0%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%2580%2599%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25AE%25B6%2F&h=be69758e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E6%8E%80%E8%B5%B7%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E6%BD%AE-%E5%B1%85%E6%B8%AF%E6%97%A5%E7%B1%8D%E6%8F%92%E7%95%AB%E5%AE%B6-%E7%95%99%E4%B8%8B%E5%9B%A0%E7%82%BA%E9%80%99%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%B6/</a><br />\n<br />\n手足既FB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mangonaoko/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmangonaoko%2F&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJAp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=c33cb5e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/mangonaoko/</a>"}]}